column2: SELECT s.specobjid, s.ra, s.dec, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid into mydb.res_xshaped_lineinfo_best7 from MyDB.sdss_in_finalbestXRGs_lineinfo AS m           JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id                OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n      JOIN SpecObjAll s ON s.specObjID = n.specObjID     --  LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS sp ON n.objID=sp.specobjID --  LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.specobjID=sp.specobjID     LEFT OUTER JOIN emissionLinesPort as g ON g.specobjID = sp.specobjID  ORDER by m.id
